UCTIONS.volume 116. release date:2018-06-19. {{ISBN|6058144903|invalid1=yes}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:1980 births]]\n", "name_user": "Rodw", "label": "safe", "comment": "Disambiguating links toFrench(link changed toFrench people) usingDisamAssist.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meta_Akkus"}
